               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡; Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡  ኢየሱስ፡, made in the government scriptorium</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="183v" facs="004"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT2701Dawit"/>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                     <note>Song of Songs, common version, with unique superscriptions and the following concluding prayer on <locus target="#162v"/>:
                  Text: <foreign xml:lang="gez"> ሰአል፡ ለነ፡ ሰሎሞን።ቅድመ፡ መንበሩ፡ ለመድኅን።
                  ኦ፡ አምላከ፡ ሰሎሞን፡።
                  አድኅነነ፡ እመ፡ ትካዝ፡ ወኃዘን።
                  ከመ፡ ታቁመነ፡ በየማን፡ ምስለ፡ አባግዒከ ቡሩካን።
                  ወአሥርቅ፡ ለነ፡ ጥበበ፡ ብርሃን።
                  ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡</foreign>
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
